OL,4,CHalfords faces 'acute' bike supply
OL,5,Cchallenges amid Covid disruption
OL,6, Halfords has warned it faces "acute"
OL,7, challenges with bike supplies after
OL,8, Covid restrictions led to surging
OL,9, demand and lockdowns in Asia hit
OL,10, manufacturers.
OL,12,FSales of bikes rose by 54.1% in the
OL,13,Fyear to 2 April as the pandemic limited
OL,14,Flocal travel and overseas holidays.
OL,16,FHalford said "pent-up" demand for bikes
OL,17,Fand continuing restrictions on foreign
OL,18,Ftrips would support future sales.
OL,20,FHowever, it added: "Supply challenges
OL,21,Ffor cycling products remain acute."
